Task 1: Generate input parameters using Dofiles/SimulationStatsBTSP.do

Task 2: Generate simulations under all counterfactuals using Fortran code

*Source code:
./Source/main.f90
./Source/import_salary.f90
./Source/salgrowth.f90
./Source/fit.f90
./Source/utilities.f90



*Input files: (generated by Dofiles/SimulationStatsBTSP.do)
./Estimation/AggregateGap/simstats.txt
./Estimation/AggregateGap/salhist.txt



*Routines:
./COMPILE
./routines/mkworkdir
./routines/getsourcedir
./routines/makeprog2


*Instructions:
	- set parameter "tenure" to 0 in ./Source/main.f90
	- set parameter "year1" to fisrt year of data in ./Source/main.f90
	- set parameter "yearT" to last year of data in ./Source/main.f90
Run the executable COMPILE
When prompted select (1) Run
When prompted specify a running directory containing three folders: Source (with the fortran source code), Estimation (with the input files) and Simulations


*Output files: (used by Dofiles/DecompositionBTSP.do)
./Simulations/AggregateGap/simulationfitxxxxxx.txt

Task 3: Generate decomposition results using Dofiles/DecompositionBTSP.do